        "14": {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "# SonarQube posture overview\n\nOverview of the security and quality findings reported by SonarQube. Learn more about [Security events ingest](https://dt-url.net/1d63p0v)."
        },
        "15": {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "### Ratings\nCurrent ratings for assessed projects, ranging from A (highest quality) to E (lowest)."
        },
        "16": {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "### Findings over time\nHistorical view of quality and security findings. Lower values indicate better results."
        },
        "17": {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "### Latest scans\nRecent SonarQube scans and their results."
        },
        "18": {
            "title": "Duplicated lines density",
            "type": "data",
            "query": "timeseries {duplications_max=max(sonarqube.code.duplication)}, \ninterval: 1d,\nfilter:{in(project, $Projects) and in(tenant,$TenantURL)}\n| fieldsAdd idx = arrayLast(duplications_max)",
            "visualization": "singleValue",
            "visualizationSettings": {
                "autoSelectVisualization": false,
                "singleValue": {
                    "labelMode": "none",
                    "label": "task.outcome",
                    "recordField": "idx",
                    "trend": {
                        "isVisible": true,
                        "upward": {
                            "Default": "var(--dt-colors-charts-loglevel-emergency-default, #ae132d)"
                        },
                        "downward": {
                            "Default": "var(--dt-colors-charts-apdex-excellent-default, #2a7453)"
                        }
                    },
                    "sparklineSettings": {
                        "showContextValues": true,
                        "showTicks": true
                    }
